#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.array_split.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.array\\_split"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.array_split.array_split:1 of
msgid "Split a tensor into multiple sub-tensors."
msgstr "将一个张量分割成多个子张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.array_split.array_split:3 of
msgid ""
"Please refer to the ``split`` documentation.  The only difference between"
" these functions is that ``array_split`` allows `indices_or_sections` to "
"be an integer that does *not* equally divide the axis. For a tensor of "
"length l that should be split into n sections, it returns l % n sub-"
"arrays of size l//n + 1 and the rest of size l//n."
msgstr ""
"请参考 ``split`` 的文档。这两个函数之间的唯一区别是 ``array_split`` 允许 "
"`indices_or_sections` 是一个不能整除轴的整数。对于长度为 l 的张量，若要将"
"其分割成 n 个部分，则会返回 l % n 个大小为 l//n + 1 的子数组，其余的大小"
"为 l//n。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.array_split.array_split:12 of
msgid ":py:obj:`split`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.array_split.array_split:13 of
msgid "Split tensor into multiple sub-tensors of equal size."
msgstr "将张量分割成多个大小相等的子张量。"

